profile: Mr. Fencee Inc is a Toronto based, Eco-friendly, maintenance-free fence company with over 7 years of experience. More importantly, Mr. Fencee Fences are made in Canada, made for Canada, withstanding the most severe weather conditions and up to 147km/hr winds.
